T01D1162:231a-1: shr'i badzra dha ra sam g'i ti bha ga b'a na sto tra:/
T01D1162:231a-3: bcom ldan 'das la bstod pa dpal rdo rje 'dzin gyi dbyangs /
T01D1162:231a-4: dpal rdo rje sems dpa' la phyag 'tshal lo //
T01D1162:231a-5: mnyam med mi g-yo mnyam nyid mchog chos can //
T01D1162:231a-6: thugs rje'i bdag nyid 'gro ba'i sdug bsngal sel //
T01D1162:231a-7: yon tan kun mnyam mtha' med dngos grub stsol //
T01D1162:231a-8: dri med mi g-yo mnyam med mchog rab chos //
T01D1162:231a-9: sems can khams la rtag mchog grub stsol ba //
T01D1162:231a-10: dngos grub mnyam dang mtha' med dpe bral ba //
T01D1162:231a-11: mnyam pa'i dpe nyid nam mkha' la med de //
T01D1162:231a-12: yon tan shas phra'i chas kyang mtshungs ma yin //
T01D1162:231a-13: rtag tu dri med thugs rje'i shugs las byung //
T01D1162:231a-14: smon lam grub pa 'gag med chos nyid can //
T01D1162:231a-15: 'gro ba'i don sgrub lhur mdzad mtha' yas pa //
T01D1162:231a-16: thugs rje'i bdag nyid rtag tu rnam par snang //
T01D1162:231a-17: dpag med mi dpogs gnas nyid legs rdzogs pa //
T01D1162:231a-18: bde gnas gshegs kyang thugs rje'i spyod mi g-yo //
T01D1162:231a-19: 'jig rten gsum la mchog gi grub stsol ba //
T01D1162:231a-20: 'gag nyid mi 'gyur ae ma'i chos nyid bzang //
T01D1162:231a-21: mchog stsol sbyin mchog nyid gnas chos nyid brnyes /
T01D1162:231a-22: 'jig rten gsum rtag dam pa stsol mchog sgrub //
T01D1162:231a-23: bde gshegs dus gsum mkhyen sgrib mi mnga' ba //
T01D1162:231a-24: kun gyi dam tshig gsum mchog grub bdag stsol //
T01D1162:231a-25: bcom ldan 'das la bstod pa dpal rdo rje 'dzin gyi dbyangs rdzogs so /
T01D1162:231a-27: // / rgya gar gyi mkhan po bidy'a ka ra pra bha dang /
